{
  "stem": "182.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "May.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were very worried, because the Russians, they-- they were very hungry for women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't dare to sleep with the German women that they encountered for fear that they may stab them in the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were very happy to see the Jewish girls, because they says, we are brothers!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are brothers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, nothing happened, thanks God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us a wagon with two-- with-- with four rubber wheels-- big, big wagon-- and a horse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- there was-- there was something different in our camp than anyplace else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were still the last transports from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was so close to the end of the war that they-- they-- some women got in who were pregnant, and who were not detected that they are pregnant.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when we were already in the Sudeten, where there we no Vernichtungslager, no extermination camps, they didn't know what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they felt by then that it will be-- that it will be a good thing if they keep these women with the babies, because they will be able to say that how good they were that they saved women with children.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to sit out to our camp, they emptied two rooms, and they brought a few Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave them beautiful lingerie, and they kept them very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had their babies there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after we were liberated, there was one woman in particular who stayed with us with a baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So on the wagon, we piled this woman and my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some girls, they collected by then a little-- some sweaters, some stuff, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went to the Germans, and they took it from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they put it on the-- on this wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
